// Probe: an assets-ONLY Worker (no "main" script). Question under test — can
// a service binding target it, and does the binding fetch serve its assets?
// Either outcome is a finding; the safe fallback is the variant-static
// pattern (one-line ASSETS forwarder script).
{
  "name": "pm-spike-variant-noscript",
  "compatibility_date": "2026-04-01",
  "assets": {
    "directory": "./public"
  }
}
